Package gameObjects

Class Fruit

java.lang.Object
gameObjects.Fruit
public class Fruit
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents fruit on the overall game in this project. The purpose of this class is to represent all information in the fruit, so that the robots can gather as much fruits as possible in the fastest and most efficient way.
Author:
Meir Nizri
